author: Peter Zimonjic,Rosemary Barton
title: Brampton Liberal MP pleads for people to stay home after testing positive for COVID-19
description: Liberal MP and registered nurse Kamal Khera has one message for Canadians since she tested positive for COVID-19: listen to the experts and stay at home.
content:
